title: Would You Pay To Get Your Child Into Schools Like Harvard, Yale, Columbia?

description:
DJ Envy wants to know if you would pay money to get your kids into schools like Harvard, Princeton, Yale?  Charlagmagne Tha God gives Donkey Of The Day to Lori Loughlin & Felicity Huffman who were busted in college bribery scandal.
